title: Diboll Lumberjacks pound Liberty

Escaping a tackle GARY STALLARD/For The Lufkin News 
Diboll’s Jamarcus Polk dances away from a would-be Liberty tackler during Friday’s game in Diboll. The Lumberjacks won the game 38-6. Posted: Saturday, September 26, 2015 1:00 am Diboll Lumberjacks pound Liberty By CODY L. HAVARD/For The Lufkin News The Lufkin News
